station

Class RobotAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • jade.core.Agent
      • station.RobotAgent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    jade.core.TimerListener, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable

    public class RobotAgent
extends jade.core.Agent
    Robot agent offers a service of "fetch" type when the agent is free. The task of this agent is to fetch a shelf commanded by the PickerAgent. They do not communicate directly with the shelves; instead, the communication is done indirectly through the picker.

    Attributes:

    • position: an instance of the class Pose with the robot position.
    • shelf_position: an instance of the class Pose with the shelf position.
    • busy: flag to reflect the status of the robot.
    • dfd: agent description with the services offered.
    • uid: argument needed for automatic creation of robot agents.

    Author:
    [DNA] Diego, Nicolas, Argentina
